title: Defense of Henneth Annûn: Ithilien Ambush - Third Age Total War Mod Gameplay
description:
Harad is marching an army to Mordor through Ithilien, than all of a suddenly arrows began raining down on their ranks!  Ithilien rangers have set up an ambush and Frodo and Sam are right in the middle of it.  They must defend Henneth Annûn.  Enjoy the Battle :D

BATTLE STARTS AT: 6:25

This is a custom Scenario made by PaladinBob

Third age Total War is a mad for Medieval 2 Total War 

If you enjoyed the video don't forget to Like and Leave a comment :D
